<style>
  section.paquetes {
    background-color: #fff;
    color: #333;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    font-family: sans-serif;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .paquetes h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #d97706;
  }

  .paquetes p {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #555;
  }

  .package-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .package-card {
    border: 2px solid #d97706;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgb(217 119 6 / 0.2);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .package-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
  }

  .package-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #b45309;
  }

  .package-price {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #d97706;
  }

  .package-features {
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    list-style-type: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    color: #555;
  }

  .package-features li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .package-cta {
    background-color: #d97706;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .package-cta:hover {
    background-color: #b45309;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .package-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="paquetes" id="paquetes">
  <h2>Nuestros Paquetes</h2>
  <p>Elige el paquete que mejor se adapte a tu evento y presupuesto.</p>

  <div class="package-grid">
    <article class="package-card">
      <h3 class="package-title">Básico</h3>
      <p class="package-price">$1,200 MXN</p>
      <ul class="package-features">
        <li>Diseño personalizado básico</li>
        <li>Enlace para compartir</li>
        <li>RSVP incluido</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="#solicitar" class="package-cta">Solicitar</a>
    </article>

    <article class="package-card">
      <h3 class="package-title">Premium</h3>
      <p class="package-price">$2,500 MXN</p>
      <ul class="package-features">
        <li>Diseño personalizado avanzado</li>
        <li>Integración con música y fotos</li>
        <li>RSVP + Confirmación por email</li>
        <li>Asistencia técnica 24/7</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="#solicitar" class="package-cta">Solicitar</a>
    </article>

    <article class="package-card">
      <h3 class="package-title">Personalizado</h3>
      <p class="package-price">Desde $4,000 MXN</p>
      <ul class="package-features">
        <li>Diseño a medida completo</li>
        <li>Funcionalidades exclusivas</li>
        <li>Soporte premium</li>
        <li>Consultoría y seguimiento</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="#solicitar" class="package-cta">Solicitar</a>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
